MMMMM. I adore Nightwish. I am obsessed with Phantom of the Opera. What a wonderful combination this is! I LOVE Marco's voice as the Phantom. It really really fits. I like it more than the actor who was the Phantom when I got to see it live. So Yay! <br>
<br>
