Wonderful! | <i>Reviewer: silverwolf</i> | <i>10/24/07</i><br>
<br>
This song is so great it got me interested in the original musical. After reading up on the plotline, I love the song even more. An excellent interpretation by nightwish.<br>
<br>
Marco's voice has just the right gravel to give a modern version, that is ear catchingly diferent from any opera version of the song. His voice gives the impression of a hated, yet pitied figure and allows you to feel empathy for the twisted soul being described.<br>
<br>
